.historycodecontest/__pycache__/
# Deploy/staging files, synced to the internal build box's xcloud_setup/ by hand
# (they carry gs:// buckets + resource-alloc names we keep out of the repo). launch.py +
# all entrypoints now live in verl/xcloud_setup/ (mirrors the internal layout); Dockerfiles
# stay in colbench/ & codecontest/.
xcloud_setup/
*/entrypoint*.sh
*/Dockerfile

# colbench: ignore transient slurm logs and the (outdated) full-1k eval dumps;
# the small cond30 eval outputs stay TRACKED for reference.
colbench/slurm_out/
colbench/selfplay/slurm_out/
colbench/runs/spec/spec_eval_selfplay_1k_*

# Empty SQLite files dropped in the repo root by in-process grading of the ColBench SQL
# problems (the GT/solver code does sqlite3.connect("<name>.db") relative to the CWD).
# Pure execution side-effects, always 0 bytes -- never source.
*.db
*.sqlite
